{"sn12.43:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 12.43 ","sn12.43:0.2":"5. Gahapativagga ","sn12.43:0.3":"Dukkhasutta ","sn12.43:1.1":"Savatthiyam viharati. ","sn12.43:1.2":"“Dukkhassa, bhikkhave, samudayanca atthangamanca desessami. ","sn12.43:1.3":"Tam sunatha, sadhukam manasi karotha, bhasissami”ti. ","sn12.43:1.4":"“Evam, bhante”ti kho te bhikkhu bhagavato paccassosum. ","sn12.43:1.5":"Bhagava etadavoca: ","sn12.43:2.1":"“Katamo ca, bhikkhave, dukkhassa samudayo? ","sn12.43:2.2":"Cakkhunca paticca rupe ca uppajjati cakkhuvinnanam. Tinnam sangati phasso. ","sn12.43:2.3":"Phassapaccaya vedana; ","sn12.43:2.4":"vedanapaccaya tanha. ","sn12.43:2.5":"Ayam kho, bhikkhave, dukkhassa samudayo. ","sn12.43:3.1":"Sotanca paticca sadde ca uppajjati sotavinnanam …pe… ","sn12.43:3.2":"ghananca paticca gandhe ca …pe… ","sn12.43:3.3":"jivhanca paticca rase ca …pe… ","sn12.43:3.4":"kayanca paticca photthabbe ca …pe… ","sn12.43:3.5":"mananca paticca dhamme ca uppajjati manovinnanam. Tinnam sangati phasso. ","sn12.43:3.6":"Phassapaccaya vedana; ","sn12.43:3.7":"vedanapaccaya tanha. ","sn12.43:3.8":"Ayam kho, bhikkhave, dukkhassa samudayo. ","sn12.43:4.1":"Katamo ca, bhikkhave, dukkhassa atthangamo? ","sn12.43:4.2":"Cakkhunca paticca rupe ca uppajjati cakkhuvinnanam. Tinnam sangati phasso. ","sn12.43:4.3":"Phassapaccaya vedana; ","sn12.43:4.4":"vedanapaccaya tanha. ","sn12.43:4.5":"Tassayeva tanhaya asesaviraganirodha upadananirodho; ","sn12.43:4.6":"upadananirodha bhavanirodho; ","sn12.43:4.7":"bhavanirodha jatinirodho; ","sn12.43:4.8":"jatinirodha jaramaranam sokaparidevadukkhadomanassupayasa nirujjhanti. ","sn12.43:4.9":"Evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa nirodho hoti. ","sn12.43:4.10":"Ayam kho, bhikkhave, dukkhassa atthangamo. ","sn12.43:5.1":"Sotanca paticca sadde ca uppajjati sotavinnanam …pe… ","sn12.43:5.2":"ghananca paticca gandhe ca …pe… ","sn12.43:5.3":"jivhanca paticca rase ca …pe… ","sn12.43:5.4":"kayanca paticca photthabbe ca …pe… ","sn12.43:5.5":"mananca paticca dhamme ca uppajjati manovinnanam. Tinnam sangati phasso. ","sn12.43:5.6":"Phassapaccaya vedana; ","sn12.43:5.7":"vedanapaccaya tanha. ","sn12.43:5.8":"Tassayeva tanhaya asesaviraganirodha upadananirodho; ","sn12.43:5.9":"upadananirodha bhavanirodho; ","sn12.43:5.10":"bhavanirodha jatinirodho; ","sn12.43:5.11":"jatinirodha jaramaranam sokaparidevadukkhadomanassupayasa nirujjhanti. ","sn12.43:5.12":"Evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa nirodho hoti. ","sn12.43:5.13":"Ayam kho, bhikkhave, dukkhassa atthangamo”ti. ","sn12.43:5.14":"Tatiyam. "}